                                <support>
                                    <p>Rectangular plaque of compact white limestone. Intact, but chipped upper left corner and with surface corrosion on the front right; some chipping also of the lower front. The left edge and the lower edge are intact, roughly finished. The top edge and teh right edge are intact but cut back behind. The rear is roughly finished.</p>
